==Japanese==
===Adjective===
'''三つ''' ([[みっつ]], ''mittsu'')

# [[three]] things [small or without a counter category]
#: 三つ (みっつ, ''mittsu'') is only used when the items counted have no specific counter category. See [[w:Japanese counter word|Wikipedia's "Japanese counter word" entry]] for details.

